<div class="clause">
  <span class="clause-num">17.</span>&ensp;<span class="clause-title">Alterations:</span>
  Tenant shall not make any alterations in or about the Premises without Landlord&rsquo;s prior written consent, including: painting, wallpapering, adding or changing locks, installing antenna or satellite dish(es), placing signs, displays or exhibits, or using screws, fastening devices, large nails or adhesive materials.
